topic.title: Version 0.5.7 site loading problem
topic.body:
The Highcharts/Highstock JavaScript on http://127.0.0.1:43110/eris.bit isn't loading with version 0.5.7 on Windows. It's working fine with earlier versions, including 0.5.6.

On further testing it seems there is a problem with downloading the content.json? It still works with this proxy: https://zeronet.maxweiss.io/eris.bit/
